    "title": "Walk-in Drive Production Engineer at JSW Steel",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Production Engineer with drive and ambition, JSW Steel in Delhi is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout JSW Steel:\nJSW Steel is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with JSW Steel!",
